//////////////////////////////////////////  MTF  Stochastic  &  RSI  Strategy  ðŸš¥  Â©ï¸  bykzis  /////////////////////////////////////////
//
//  ***  Inspired  by  "Binance  CHOP  Dashboard"  from  @Cazimiro  and  "RSI  MTF  Table"  from  @mobester16  ***  and  LOT  OF  COPY  of  Indicator-Jones  MTF  Scanner
